  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Nightwalker</i>, you play as an aspiring investigator who sets out to explore a rumored deadly forest. As you drive closer, doubt begins to creep in. This short horror adventure game blends classic horror elements with unique gameplay features.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short horror story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tension-filled atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive ambience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrifying creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small puzzles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare for a chilling experience!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Nightwalker</i>, you play as an aspiring investigator who sets out to explore a rumored deadly forest. As you drive closer, doubt begins to creep in. This short horror adventure game blends classic horror elements with unique gameplay features.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short horror story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tension-filled atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive ambience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrifying creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small puzzles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare for a chilling experience!</strong></p>",
